{"tid":720913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本電競代表隊不受日本奧委會承認，無法出席亞運開幕式","createTime":"2018-06-28T09:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T05:17:00.000Z","uid":134071,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cff82c59d642291f84edace1d520241e5b415ce9","tid":720913,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T09:45:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.ptt.cc/bbs/C_Chat/M.1530177476.A.5E9.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FC_Chat%2FM.1530177476.A.5E9.html&d=FnQ%2F9mtAayapiHTGFvsBm54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=b65cd6ab\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ptt.cc/bbs/C_Chat/M.1530177476.A.5E9.html</a><br />\n<br />\n作者AkihisaYoshi (AkihisaYoshi)<br />\n看板C_Chat<br />\n標題[閒聊] 日本電競代表隊不受日本奧會承認，將無法出席亞運開幕式<br />\n時間Thu Jun 28 17:17:51 2018<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://goo.gl/SXA4dQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FSXA4dQ&d=FnQ%2F9mtAayapiHTGFvsBm54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=7ecd8319\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://goo.gl/SXA4dQ</a><br />\n<br />\n簡單說就是，雖然日本這次在今年雅加達亞運的電競預賽中有三人脫穎而出<br />\n<br />\n但是日本奧會(JOC)並不承認日本電競代表隊是由JOC正式派遣的日本代表<br />\n<br />\nJOC表示：「因為報名程序上需要JOC的蓋章，我們只是幫忙蓋這個章而已。日本電競代表隊是由日本電競連合(JeSU)所派遣的，與我們無關。」<br />\n<br />\n由於這樣，因為日本電競代表隊並非由JOC正式派遣的日本代表，不會留在正式紀錄中，所以沒辦法拿到日本隊的團隊制服、同時於亞運期間選手在當地也拿不到生活津貼、<br />\n<br />\n而且不能出席亞運開/閉幕式、甚至於亞運期間能否入住選手村都還是問題...<br />\n<br />\n(JOC表示關於選手村這部分，能否入村是交由印尼亞運組委會判斷，不關我的事)"},{"pid":"d8d1998cad42c04446ca010f5c4202a95c228ad2","tid":720913,"uid":78971,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T09:55:01.000Z","msg":"把好關呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由得其他國家嘅年輕人沉迷電莖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a154ad6b26c5422c6e241d4295dbfbbf2131776d","tid":720913,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:04:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295eeca40e6a25aff7ae5cc5ee7f310436a66132","tid":720913,"uid":177590,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:09:15.000Z","msg":"咁贏左咪撚上日本旗，日本國啦<br />\n上自己隊旗，再搭首鳥之詩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4363311820fff7fe6594df9d233b6d2f42e2045","tid":720913,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:50:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c9a2f252d751517239740cf3e1d6a725e4f934","tid":720913,"uid":75139,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:57:10.000Z","msg":"開幕式係咩泳式？"},{"pid":"bcc96e4facb8c6260b7b374a4502aa85616fe4ed","tid":720913,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T14:10:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8eb72d719235794b72059797c24f4e78b8fd5f8","tid":720913,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T15:00:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0fc171754a2a0720bd0cafc7f01ac30837522de8","tid":720913,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:58:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe006084418e92773a9e42b4dde1519f7f67e81","tid":720913,"uid":28076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e8eb72d719235794b72059797c24f4e78b8fd5f8","tid":720913,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T15:00:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:00:36.000Z","msg":"美國=垃圾國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1136b14b3f266b90c1273edfbc0ecd17f0130a4","tid":720913,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8d1998cad42c044